'''哈克市场'''（Hackescher Markt）得名于城市军队总监冯·哈克，是德国柏林市中心的一个广场，位于[[奥拉宁堡大街|奥拉宁堡大街]]的末端.这是一个文化中心，以夜生活著称<ref>{{cite book |title=Nights in the Big City: Paris, Berlin, London 1840-1930 |last=Schlör |first=Joachim |year=1998 |publisher=Reaktion Books |isbn=186189015X |pages=p. 32 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=JSg9bBgWpbEC&pg=PA32&dq=%22Hackescher+Markt%22+%2Bberlin+-hotel+-bahn&num=100&as_brr=3&sig=5nBAZCosmhU1TjDRauULoBHZZRs |access-date=2009-03-08 |archive-date=2015-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121032259/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=JSg9bBgWpbEC&pg=PA32&dq=%22Hackescher+Markt%22+%2Bberlin+-hotel+-bahn&num=100&as_brr=3&sig=5nBAZCosmhU1TjDRauULoBHZZRs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

哈克市场也是一个轻轨火车站的名称，最初名为Börse,在东德时期称为[[马克思-恩格斯广场|马克思-恩格斯广场]]<ref>{{cite book |title=After Unity: Reconfiguring German Identities |last=Jarausch |first=Konrad Hugo |year=1997 |publisher=Berghahn Books |isbn=1571810404 |pages=p. 132 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=-7k9l55-IukC&pg=PA132&dq=%22Hackescher+Markt%22+%2Bberlin+-hotel+-bahn&num=100&as_brr=3&sig=Yd5Tu6pCzshoWettUGmoNo-4ORQ |access-date=2009-03-08 |archive-date=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324033141/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=-7k9l55-IukC&pg=PA132&dq=%22Hackescher+Markt%22+%2Bberlin+-hotel+-bahn&num=100&as_brr=3&sig=Yd5Tu6pCzshoWettUGmoNo-4ORQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

